Well folks, don't let it be said that I warned you, this is not a literary site.  Our newest writer expresses the same frustration that I feel. That we are at log heads with each other and need to move on.  <br><br>
The fact that some of you think of me as a lighting rod should amuse me, but it does not. It fills me with grief.<br>
Too many of our generation died, in a cause without honor,<br>
that it DOES NOT need to be faught again, by old farts 30 years later.  I agree with our anon poet, let it go. Lets move on.  Can the rest of you agree?  Did we learn NOTHING from Viet Nam? Did we learn that GOD DAMN you won't take my son into that slaughter machine?  <br><br>
When will you guys wake up?<br><br>
doc
